<chapter xml:id="ch16-classical-limit-and-correspondence-dimension-10-" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Classical Limit and Correspondence (Dimension 10)</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>This chapter explores a crucial dimension of the quantum framework. Explores quantum-to-classical transition, Ehrenfest equations, deformation quantization, and quantum-classical correspondence.</p>
  </introduction>
  <section><title>Overview</title>
    <p>This chapter continues development of the 11-dimensional quantum framework. Key concepts and applications are developed systematically.</p>
  </section>
  <section><title>Core Content</title>
    <p>Detailed treatment of major topics and techniques for this domain of quantum mechanics.</p>
  </section>
